      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو جَعْفَرٍ ع مَنْ قَالَ فِی رُکُوعِهِ وَ سُجُودِهِ وَ قِیَامِهِ اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ آلِ مُحَمَّدٍ کَتَبَ اللَّهُ لَهُ ذَلِکَ بِمِثْلِ الرُّکُوعِ وَ السُّجُودِ وَ الْقِیَامِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1.  Imam  Muhammad  Baqir  (a.s.)  says,  “One  who  recites: Allaahumma     s’alli     a’laa     muh’ammadinw     wa     aali muh’ammad in his Ruku, his Sajdah and his Qiyam, Allah writes for him a reward like that of Ruku, Sajdah or Qiyam.”"
        ]
      }
